      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到参与者命名里用了kikwi-core，还有括号里的Logistics_FleetManagement标注。另外提交数据时，Repository是直接操作MongoDB吗？",
