      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Repository就是ProcessExecutionRepository，它负责和MongoDB打交道。事务里要做三件事：更新流程实例、处理可执行任务、把关键事件写入event_outbox表。",
